Package: simCAT
Title: Implements Computerized Adaptive Testing Simulations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Alexandre Jaloto [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5291-1768>)
    Ricardo Primi [ths]
Description: Computerized Adaptive Testing simulations with dichotomous items. Selects items with Maximum Fisher Information method or randomly, with or without constraints (content balancing and item exposure control).
